{"tid":1476553,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"2019 Sundance FFHK 辛丹斯電影節：香港 集中討論區","createTime":"2019-08-16T00:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T13:46:53.000Z","uid":4260,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e8bc217bf448f590c12d50d34792d09a6b48242b","tid":1476553,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T00:27:31.000Z","msg":"🎬 片單公布！<br />\n<br />\n2019 「辛丹斯電影節：香港」今年繼續為影迷精心挑選12部高質素獨立電影，包括：<br />\n<br />\n開幕電影 －《寶貝童年》(Honey Boy)<br />\n《少年亞當的煩惱》(Adam)<br />\n《扭計魔術師》(The Amazing Johnathan Documentary)<br />\n《阿波羅11號》(Apollo 11)<br />\n《心思思，問下性博士》(Ask Dr. Ruth)<br />\n《我的馬拉松日記》(Brittany Runs a Marathon)<br />\n《刑與愛的邊緣》(Clemency)<br />\n《撒旦萬萬歲》(Hail Satan?)<br />\n《何處是吾家》(The Last Black Man in San Francisco)<br />\n《老師．喪屍．小BB》(Little Monsters)<br />\n《盧斯的秘密》(Luce) <br />\n《月光奏鳴曲：無聲的三樂章》(Moonlight Sonata: Deafness in Three Movements)<br />\n<br />\n📌 門票將於8月19日起公開發售，星影匯VIP Metropolitans會員更可於即日起尊享優先購票。<br />\n詳情：<a href=\"http://hk.sundance.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.sundance.org&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEr7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=d2fca7f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk.sundance.org</a><br />\n<br />\n2019「辛丹節電影節：香港」<br />\n9.19 - 10.1 星影匯舉行"},{"pid":"2217e2ead7684b8eaa0d260d0feb4325bf815862","tid":1476553,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T00:31:51.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<br />\n幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行過路過入嚟望下，千載難逢嘅大好機會！！十八區we connect，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">823人鏈823人鏈823人鏈</span></span></strong>，百萬人齊築香江路！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［和理非升級］一生人一次嘅機會嚟喇！！！！想唔想上Buzzfeed 9GAG？！？！？！？！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475842\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475842</a>"},{"p